{"tid":687330,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：旭屋水產","createTime":"2018-06-02T07:12:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T04:09:00.000Z","uid":181719,"like":3,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2e48207943a19e46e7fef6d88bd944db24386368","tid":687330,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"就朋友放工地點，喺鰂魚涌附近搵野食，我就提議去試吓呢間大隱隱於市嘅日本野，諗住咁隱蔽一定好靜啱傾偈。一入門口，直頭靜到離哂譜，又係包場。可惜唔記得影相。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就唔係太喜歡食生野嘅，嗌咗個蒲燒鰻魚飯定食。定食喎，諗住影相一定靚，點知侍應話鰻魚要燒，上哂湯同冷盤比我食住先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/150553_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F150553_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=10fb40bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麵豉湯係大路貨色，炸蠔就外脆內嫩完全唔腥，幾好食。沙律上面果幾粒唔知係咩黎，但口感都好唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n等到鰻魚飯上，其實都唔係好耐。望落份量都唔少，但我就不嬲貴精不貴多嘅，要食過先知。啱啱燒出黎，夠熱夠香口唔在講，肉質夠嫩而且骨刺夠軟，好過好多其他地方，骨刺硬要逐條吐出黎，甚至根本食唔到。骨刺軟硬，究竟同條鰻魚新鮮度定烹調方法有關，我是唔識分的，總之佢係好食。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/150654_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F150654_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2c3aa216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/150717_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F150717_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6115fa34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外飯面上仲有甜蛋幾舊，稍為淡味，但都算唔錯。青瓜同酸羅白都係基本野啦。最後食佢果粒芝麻湯圓咁嘅東西，已經飽哂。148蚊，晚飯黎講算抵食。呢間野真係冇咩可以挑剔，如果唔係最近少咗比人話係打手，都唔敢出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7716b9c6cde0fa042b45e91363f2fb3372e62dd3","tid":687330,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f132f191d49eecec0fb126f1bf799003c1098c09","tid":687330,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7716b9c6cde0fa042b45e91363f2fb3372e62dd3","tid":687330,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:28:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:50:11.000Z","msg":"巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1457c597922b0b81b1452a62c9794433f4ab4ba5","tid":687330,"uid":54124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:25:28.000Z","msg":"咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302433a6403051a3dd3de9ceb8e85d9838891fcc","tid":687330,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1457c597922b0b81b1452a62c9794433f4ab4ba5","tid":687330,"uid":54124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:25:28.000Z","msg":"咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"間餐廳？旭屋水產，鰂魚涌b出口過天橋"},{"pid":"99bb733b789b87d9064760109a422985e274e603","tid":687330,"uid":6427,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/094958_2e4776bdfdda3b92a03ee6c410795145.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F094958_2e4776bdfdda3b92a03ee6c410795145.png&h=bbe4cd06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個月有次中午做野經過去食<br />\nLunch 食好高質呀 <br />\n好鐘意佢既甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碎吞拿魚好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768210321740b57aa7ed565ee764c06f6c07aeda","tid":687330,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"個樣唔似即燒果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 似預先整好左一包包買返黎果啲加返熱⋯平時食即燒果啲冇咁乾淨，實有小小黑碳屎之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92d5a62fbb82045fe0bff1b87c84774b41df4a6","tid":687330,"uid":128930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"768210321740b57aa7ed565ee764c06f6c07aeda","tid":687330,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"個樣唔似即燒果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 似預先整好左一包包買返黎果啲加返熱⋯平時食即燒果啲冇咁乾淨，實有小小黑碳屎之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:56:39.000Z","msg":"應該係啦，百幾蚊就想食新鮮鰻魚"},{"pid":"c5be584e0c739b5df8c201659c3034c9b18c4b4a","tid":687330,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"99bb733b789b87d9064760109a422985e274e603","tid":687330,"uid":6427,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T01:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/03/094958_2e4776bdfdda3b92a03ee6c410795145.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F03%2F094958_2e4776bdfdda3b92a03ee6c410795145.png&h=bbe4cd06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個月有次中午做野經過去食<br />\nLunch 食好高質呀 <br />\n好鐘意佢既甜品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n碎吞拿魚好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 擺盤好靚<br />\nlunch好似平啲，但我唔喺果頭做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df89119c39bed04acf6ba6c46559d3344711ef9b"